---
import { ArrowRightIcon, BookOpenIcon } from "@heroicons/react/24/outline";
---

<section class="bg-primary-950 py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <div
      class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-primary-300/20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 via-primary-600 to-primary-500 px-6 py-14 shadow-[0_24px_80px_rgba(74,6,5,0.35)] sm:px-10 lg:px-16"
    >
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div
          class="flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-neutral-50/25 bg-neutral-50/10 backdrop-blur"
        >
          <BookOpenIcon className="h-10 w-10 text-neutral-50" />
        </div>

        <h2
          class="mt-8 font-title text-3xl font-extrabold text-neutral-50 sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
        >
          Comienza tu aventura en CSS Quest AI
        </h2>

        <p
          class="mt-6 max-w-3xl font-text text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-50/90 sm:text-xl"
        >
          Explora la documentación del juego, conoce su propuesta educativa y da
          el siguiente paso para empezar a practicar CSS con una experiencia
          guiada por IA.
        </p>

        <div
          class="mt-10 flex w-full flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:w-auto sm:flex-row"
        >
          <a
            href="/gdd"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 px-8 py-4 font-text text-lg font-semibold text-primary-700 transition hover:bg-primary-100"
          >
            <BookOpenIcon className="h-6 w-6" />
            Explorar GDD
          </a>

          <a
            href="/login"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-50/35 bg-transparent px-8 py-4 font-text text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-50 transition hover:bg-neutral-50/10"
          >
            <ArrowRightIcon className="h-6 w-6" />
            Iniciar ahora
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
